Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:35.93,kasij,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be20}夢を見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:38.39,kasij,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be20}歓びへと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.47,0:23:43.35,kasij,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be20}人はいつか辿り着ける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:50.95,kasij,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be20}子供の瞳で貴方は信じた
